data.description: FIRST FLOOR, FULLY FURNISHED and MOVE IN READY! Welcome Home to this Meticulously Maintained GROUND Floor Condominium located in the highly sought after Community of Imperial Cove. This Unit Boasts Ultra LOW HOA fees at only $270 per Month making it Extremely affordable as either a Vacation Spot or Primary Residence. This one of a kind property Boasts many upgrades to include an Updated KITCHEN, STAINLESS APPLIANCES, NEW BATH Vanity, Toilet, Updated Flooring, Newer Hot Water Heater, and Totally Tiled Lanai. This Home is FULLY FURNISHED to include but not limited to: a Pier 1 Jamaica Bedroom Set, Cindy Crawford Living Room Chairs, Leather Couch, Glass Dining Table, and ECT..! This Spacious Home is Conveniently located on the First Level, less than (1) Block from the Community Clubhouse. Imperial Cove is Clearwater’s Premier 55+ Gated Community; a Private Oasis that allows its residents to Live an active lifestyle with a Full Fitness Center, Sauna Room, Billiard Room, Convention Hall, Putting Green, Shuffle Board Court(s), On site Fishing Pier; Cove Front: Grills, Kitchenette, and Olympic Sized Heated Pool. The Community Cove features a large dock where you can watch the Dolphins and Manatees play year round. Schedule your private showing today and see all the features that this Unit and Imperial Cove has to offer.
data.whatILove: I LOVE all of the Updates, Ultra Low HOA Fees, and the Convenient Ground Floor Unit location. The best part is Imperial Cove itself, It's a Private Oasis that is close to everything! The grounds are Extremely Well Manicured and Meticulously Maintained. The numerous community events, the Gym, the Billiard room, and the Heated Pool allow me to live a lifestyle as active as I choose to be. I LOVE this Unit and LOVE Imperial Cove!
